In a job step, import the adaptor and chain its operations. Each operation reads and writes to job state, so the response from one becomes the input to the next:

import { insertDocuments, findDocuments, updateDocument } from "@openfn/language-mongodb";

findDocuments({ /* params */ });

The Snippets tab has 1 ready-to-paste example grouped by category — start there rather than from scratch.
